--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
I: improvement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.3.2 (2018-07-19)
I: Shell script improvements

* Version 2.3.1 (2018-07-12)
I: Generate a random minute for the cronjob

* Version 2.3.0 (2018-07-01)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.2-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE

* Version 2.2.0 (2018-05-22)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 2.1.2 (2018-04-24)
I: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 2.1.1 (2018-04-04)
I: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 2.1.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 2.0.1 (2018-02-24)
B: Correct term in state filter

* Version 2.0.0 (2018-02-20)
I: Simplify and improve Ansible role

* Version 1.1.1 (2017-10-18)
I: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 1.1.0 (2017-08-26)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE

* Version 1.0.0 (2017-08-01)
I: Stabilize, improve and cleanup Ansible role

* Version 0.5.1 (2017-04-16)
I: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 0.5.0 (2016-10-14)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE

* Version 0.4.2 (2016-09-03)
I: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 0.4.1 (2016-05-29)
I: Improve FreeBSD support

* Version 0.4.0 (2016-05-21)
F: Add support for Ansible 2.0

* Version 0.3.0 (2016-04-09)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.2-RELEASE

* Version 0.2.2 (2016-04-02)
I: Update support information for OpenBSD 5.9

* Version 0.2.1 (2016-03-08)
I: Minor script improvements

* Version 0.2.0 (2016-01-21)
F: Drop support for OS family 'Gentoo'

* Version 0.1.4 (2015-11-17)
I: Add missing Ansible tags

* Version 0.1.3 (2015-08-23)
I: Improve Shell exit codes

* Version 0.1.2 (2015-03-05)
I: Minor script improvements

* Version 0.1.1 (2015-02-03)
I: Improve ZFS scrub script

* Version 0.1.0 (2015-01-16)
F: Initial release
